[
    {
        "text": "A resume without a cover letter is like a burger without a bun.",
        "startTime": 6083,
        "endTime": 9321,
        "slowStartTime": 9275,
        "slowEndTime": 14207
    },
    {
        "text": "If you really wanted a job from somebody,...",
        "startTime": 9690,
        "endTime": 11667,
        "slowStartTime": 14685,
        "slowEndTime": 17726
    },
    {
        "text": "...you wouldn't send them a burger without a bun, would you? ",
        "startTime": 11791,
        "endTime": 14015,
        "slowStartTime": 17837,
        "slowEndTime": 21247
    },
    {
        "text": "Of course not.",
        "startTime": 14289,
        "endTime": 15159,
        "slowStartTime": 21583,
        "slowEndTime": 22964
    },
    {
        "text": "You will need: a computer, typewriter, or some other mechanical writing device...",
        "startTime": 16028,
        "endTime": 20663,
        "slowStartTime": 24192,
        "slowEndTime": 31220
    },
    {
        "text": "...a cover letter should never be handwritten.",
        "startTime": 20812,
        "endTime": 22643,
        "slowStartTime": 31368,
        "slowEndTime": 34189
    },
    {
        "text": "Step one: Address the letter to a specific person.",
        "startTime": 23145,
        "endTime": 26029,
        "slowStartTime": 34867,
        "slowEndTime": 39269
    },
    {
        "text": "Writing \"to whom it may concern\" is lazy. ",
        "startTime": 26342,
        "endTime": 28463,
        "slowStartTime": 39663,
        "slowEndTime": 42920
    },
    {
        "text": "Tracking down the right person shows real moxie.",
        "startTime": 28728,
        "endTime": 31193,
        "slowStartTime": 43242,
        "slowEndTime": 47015
    },
    {
        "text": "If you're unsure who to write, call the company and ask.",
        "startTime": 32251,
        "endTime": 35002,
        "slowStartTime": 48526,
        "slowEndTime": 52728
    },
    {
        "text": "Make sure you get their exact title and correct spelling of their name.",
        "startTime": 35289,
        "endTime": 38210,
        "slowStartTime": 53084,
        "slowEndTime": 57540
    },
    {
        "text": "Step two: Open your letter with a short introduction that gets right to the point;...",
        "startTime": 38861,
        "endTime": 42695,
        "slowStartTime": 58441,
        "slowEndTime": 64268
    },
    {
        "text": "...say what position you're after and how you found out about it.",
        "startTime": 43057,
        "endTime": 45525,
        "slowStartTime": 64736,
        "slowEndTime": 68513
    },
    {
        "text": "Step three: Demonstrate that you understand what the company does,...",
        "startTime": 46345,
        "endTime": 49761,
        "slowStartTime": 69667,
        "slowEndTime": 74867
    },
    {
        "text": "...and show enthusiasm for whatever that is.",
        "startTime": 49872,
        "endTime": 51987,
        "slowStartTime": 74958,
        "slowEndTime": 78206
    },
    {
        "text": "Read through the company's website to find details you can mention in your letter.",
        "startTime": 52889,
        "endTime": 56112,
        "slowStartTime": 79483,
        "slowEndTime": 84393
    },
    {
        "text": "Step four: Relate your past work experience to the current opening.",
        "startTime": 56777,
        "endTime": 60219,
        "slowStartTime": 85315,
        "slowEndTime": 90554
    },
    {
        "text": "Don't count on employers to connect the dots and realize how your previous jobs are relevant.",
        "startTime": 60569,
        "endTime": 64675,
        "slowStartTime": 91004,
        "slowEndTime": 97238
    },
    {
        "text": "Step five: If you're responding to a job posting,...",
        "startTime": 65301,
        "endTime": 67917,
        "slowStartTime": 98102,
        "slowEndTime": 102101
    },
    {
        "text": "...adapt your writing to address specific things mentioned in the post.",
        "startTime": 68138,
        "endTime": 71163,
        "slowStartTime": 102357,
        "slowEndTime": 106970
    },
    {
        "text": "Keep your cover letter short and concise.",
        "startTime": 71897,
        "endTime": 73932,
        "slowStartTime": 107995,
        "slowEndTime": 111123
    },
    {
        "text": "It shouldn't be longer than a page.",
        "startTime": 74136,
        "endTime": 75629,
        "slowStartTime": 111354,
        "slowEndTime": 113669
    },
    {
        "text": "A few brief paragraphs is enough.",
        "startTime": 75922,
        "endTime": 77520,
        "slowStartTime": 114033,
        "slowEndTime": 116505
    },
