        "startTime": 82865,
        "endTime": 84167,
        "slowStartTime": 124447,
        "slowEndTime": 126476
    },
    {
        "text": "Step seven: After thanking your reader, sign off with a suitable closing, like \"Sincerely\" or \"Best.\"",
        "startTime": 84847,
